data.description: Super cute 3B/2B/2G single story home in a great location, on a cul-de-sac lot! Charming interior with vaulted ceiling in the main living space anchored by a feature wall fireplace with beautiful brick hearth. Remodeled kitchen w/large breakfast room, solid stone quartz counters, deep well sink & new appliances all enhanced by the under cabinet lighting. Cozy rooms throughout the home that are well-sized w/spacious closets. Principal bedroom is large w/an en-suite bath. The backyard has plenty of space and is perfect for entertaining your guests with extended patio. Whole house w/hardy plank siding, double pane windows w/2" faux blinds, newer roof less than 2yrs old, 8" blown insulation & whole home generator! Easy access to Beltway 8, with plenty of shopping, restaurants and entertainment in close proximity. Come and see this adorable property today!
